OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FThe Assisted Dying Bill for England
OL,7,Fand Wales is set to return to
OL,8,Fparliament after an MP announced that
OL,9,Fshe would reintroduce it.
OL,11,FLabour MP Lauren Edwards said she
OL,12,Fwanted to give the legislation another
OL,13,Fchance after it ran out of time in the
OL,14,FHouse of Lords on its first attempt.
OL,16,FThe MP for Rochester and Strood came
OL,17,Fsecond in the private members ballot,
OL,18,Fin which MPs' names are drawn at
OL,19,Frandom to determine who gets a chance
OL,20,Fto introduce a bill of their own
OL,21,Fdesign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
