OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781525476
OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FEdwards voted in favour of assisted
OL,7,Fdying when Kim Leadbeater tried to
OL,8,Fpass her bill in the last session of
OL,9,Fparliament.
OL,11,FThe plan now is to bring back exactly
OL,12,Fthe same legislation, in the hope that
OL,13,FMPs will back it a second time.
OL,15,FLabour MP Lauren Edwards announces
OL,16,Fthat she will reintroduce Kim
OL,17,FLeadbeater's Assisted Dying Bill
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781525476
OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FEdwards told ITV News: "I thought very
OL,7,Flong and hard about it. I spoke to a
OL,8,Flot of people. I spoke to members of
OL,9,Fmy family who are in Australia who
OL,10,Fhave experience of assisted dying.
OL,12,F"And I was very comfortable with the
OL,13,Flegislation and really hoped that it
OL,14,Fcould have passed its parliamentary
OL,15,Fstages last time.
OL,17,F"I think the frustration that I've
OL,18,Ffelt is also widely felt amongst other
OL,19,Fparliamentarians and members of the
OL,20,Fpublic - that this process has been
OL,21,Ffrustrated by a small minority."
OL,26,@nD@XOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
