OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FIn April, the Assisted Dying Bill ran
OL,7,Fout of time after peers tabled more
OL,8,Fthan a thousand amendments to the
OL,9,Fbill, with the majority put forward by
OL,10,Fjust seven lords.
OL,12,FThe behaviour drew accusations of
OL,13,Fdeliberate time-wasting ` known as
OL,14,Ffilibustering - which opponents of the
OL,15,Fbill strenuously denied.
OL,17,FThey insist that the bill was unsafe
OL,18,Fand required serious amendment,
OL,19,Fblaming supporters for designing what
OL,20,Fthey considered to be a flawed piece
OL,21,Fof legislation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781525476
OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FAmong the opponents of the bill, which
OL,7,Fsaw opinion sharply divided on each
OL,8,Fside of the Commons last time, is
OL,9,FLabour MP Ashley Dalton.
OL,11,FIn a statement on Sunday night, she
OL,12,Fsaid: "I'm deeply concerned that
OL,13,Fsupporters are bringing the assisted
OL,14,Fdying bill back.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781525476
OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,F"Voters put us in power to reduce the
OL,7,Fcost of living and fix the NHS. We
OL,8,Fhave debated this deeply divisive and
OL,9,Fflawed assisted dying bill for over a
OL,10,Fyear and supporters have refused to
OL,11,Flisten or to make the necessary
OL,12,Fchanges.
OL,14,F"This bill would hand sweeping
OL,15,Funchecked powers over life and death
OL,16,Fand our NHS to future governments,
OL,17,Fwhatever their political persuasion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781525476
OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,F"We should not be using more of our
OL,7,Flimited time and political capital on
OL,8,Fsomething that simply isn't safe or a
OL,9,Fpriority for the people who put us in
OL,10,Fpower."
OL,12,FThe Lords now have an 'opportunity' to
OL,13,Ffinish scrutinising the abandoned
OL,14,Flegislation, Lauren Edwards says
OL,16,FIf the House of Lords fails to pass
OL,17,Fthe bill again, supporters say they
OL,18,Fwill fall back on the Parliament Acts,
OL,19,Fwhich allow a bill to bypass peers on
OL,20,Fits second attempt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781525476
OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FEdwards said: "I hope we won't need to
OL,7,Fuse those Parliament Act powers.
OL,9,F"I'm hoping that the House of Lords
OL,10,Fwill do the job that they're there to
OL,11,Fdo and that they do a really good job
OL,12,Fof, which is to scrutinise and refine
OL,13,Flegislation that has been passed by
OL,14,Fthe House of Commons.
OL,16,F"It's an opportunity for them to
OL,17,Ffinish that job that was started many,
OL,18,Fmany, many months ago and which
OL,19,Funfortunately had to be abandoned."
OL,26,@nD@OOUqD@AOUxD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
