OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe road ahead is uncertain for the
OL,12,Fbill, however, with a handful of
OL,13,Fprevious supporters expressing doubt
OL,14,Fin recent weeks about resorting to the
OL,15,FParliament Act powers.
OL,17,FA small number have said that they
OL,18,Fwould not favour bypassing the House
OL,19,Fof Lords.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781525476
OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FBut Edwards insists that others have
OL,7,Fbeen outraged by the failure of peers
OL,8,Fto reach a vote on the bill at the
OL,9,Flast attempt, persuading some
OL,10,Fopponents to back the bill this time.
OL,12,FLauren Edwards express her
OL,13,F'frustration' at the halting of
OL,14,Fdemocratic process by a 'small
OL,15,Fminority'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781525476
OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,F"I've heard from a number of MPs who
OL,7,Fmaybe weren't originally in favour of
OL,8,Fthe assisted dying legislation, but
OL,9,Factually have been rather frustrated
OL,10,Fby the actions of the House of Lords
OL,11,Fand are saying that they would vote
OL,12,Ffor it to go back to the Lords to
OL,13,Ffinish that process," she said.
OL,15,F"They value our democratic processes
OL,16,Fand they don't want people to lose
OL,17,Feven more trust in our political
OL,18,Fsystem because the will (of MPs) is
OL,19,Fnot being respected by the second
OL,20,Fchamber, which isn't elected."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@UO]wD@AOUzD@YpmzD@`pn|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
