OL,3,CAssisted Dying Bill to return to
OL,4,Cparliament for second attempt
OL,6,FEdwards is expected to reintroduce the
OL,7,Fbill to parliament later this summer,
OL,8,Fbut MPs aren't expected to vote on it
OL,9,Funtil the autumn.
OL,11,FSince Leadbeater first introduced her
OL,12,Fbill, both the Isle of Man and Jersey
OL,13,Fhave legalised assisted dying,
OL,14,Fbecoming the first two places in the
OL,15,FBritish Isles to do so.
OL,17,FScotland voted in February to reject a
OL,18,Fsimilar bill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
